This directory contains Alembic migrations for the Midnight Walk server.

Run migrations with:

```
alembic -c midnight_walk/alembic.ini upgrade head
```

Ensure `DATABASE_URL` (or `MIDNIGHT_DB_PATH` for SQLite) is set so the migrations
connect to the correct database. Alembic will automatically pick up the URL via
`midnight_walk.database.get_database_url()`.
